COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 1200, L.D. 1789
1 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
2 number to read consecutively.
3 SUMMARY
44 This amendment replaces the bill and changes the title. It clarifies the education
55 requirements to take the licensing examination and to qualify for licensure as a certified
66 public accountant.
